          <section data-auto-animate>
            <h4>Key Terms</h4>
            <dl>
              <dt>Selection</dt>
              <dd>
                The ability of a program to choose which code to execute based
                on a condition.
              </dd>
              <dt>If Statement</dt>
              <dd>
                A fundamental control flow structure that allows a program to
                execute a block of code only if a specified condition is <AstroCode
                  code="true"
                  lang="javascript"
                  inline
                  theme="material-theme-ocean"
                />. It consists of the if keyword, a condition, and a code
                block.
              </dd>
            </dl>
          </section>
          <section data-auto-animate>
            <h4>Key Terms</h4>
            <dl>
              <dt>Condition</dt>
              <dd>
                A logical expression that evaluates to a Boolean value (<AstroCode
                  code="true"
                  lang="javascript"
                  inline
                  theme="material-theme-ocean"
                /> or <AstroCode
                  code="false"
                  lang="javascript"
                  inline
                  theme="material-theme-ocean"
                />). It determines whether the code inside an if statement's
                code block will be executed.
              </dd>
              <dt>Code Block</dt>
              <dd>
                A group of one or more programming statements enclosed in curly
                braces (<AstroCode
                  code="{ }"
                  lang="javascript"
                  inline
                  theme="material-theme-ocean"
                />). In an <AstroCode
                  code="if"
                  lang="javascript"
                  inline
                  theme="material-theme-ocean"
                /> statement, this block of code is executed when the condition is
                met.
              </dd>
            </dl>
          </section>
